title: the.fugitive.414.dvdrip.xvid-ositv
description:
The Fugitive.S04E14.The Evil Men Do.DVDRip by OSiTV (with English subtitles)


For those who wish to play the show on stand-alone DVD players, I'm continuing to upload the episodes in avi format, including English subtitles.

Meanwhile, the upload of the mkv files has been finished - the mkv files are slightly better in video quality with higher resolution, but they can't be played on stand-alone DVD players.
